Plan:
1. Build a self-contained verifier around the live periphery, floor, getter, router, and NFT/token interfaces.
2. Implement runtime discovery for supported candidate collections, then try the direct existing fragment-balance path first and re-fragment claimed NFTs into attacker profit tokens.
3. Add a best-effort existing-ETH path using the same vulnerable `buyAndClaimVault` flow, but leave profit at zero when no pre-existing stranded balance makes positive net profit possible at this fork state.
4. Compile-check the source locally if the workspace permits it.
