I’ve narrowed the viable proof path to: exploit any pre-existing periphery fragment balance, claim an NFT to this verifier, then fragment that NFT back to realize profit in an existing on-chain fragment token. I’m writing the verifier as a single self-contained Solidity file so it compiles without depending on a missing local project scaffold.
